bookmarks.description: Look up anyone's stats. You can also view a players xp history and status on important quests. This app will also open when you press alt+1 over any rightclick option on a player.
An easy way to view the Runescape Wiki. This app will also open if you press alt+1 over any examine option in-game.
This app allows you to keep track of your map and keys in dungeoneering. You can also connect to your teammates to always stay up to date.
This app will keep track of your xp rates in real time.
Log any drops using this app by simply pressing alt+1 over the pick up or use option on your loot. You can also share your droplog online.
The all-in-one clue solver. Simple click the unlock button when any treasure trials clue or puzzle is visible on your screen and the solution will be shown.

This app will alert whenever you have to click on runescape when doing anything afk.
It alerts when you stop skilling, your hp is low or your potions run out and much more.
Keep track of when D&D's and other things start. This app will alert you when the voice of seren changes, warbands starts, your farming patch completes and much more.
This app calculates and tracks the correct tackle combinations in fish flingers.
Shows the best answer to give to meg in player owned ports. Lazyness has reached a new level.
A simple timer to keep track of your farming patches. This timer will predict growth ticks for added accuracy.
An easy and quick way to get color codes for your max or completionists cape. This app will show color codes for anything visible on your screen.
A simple stopwatch and countdown timer.
A simple notepad for use while scaping.
A simple world map that can stay open while you run around the world.
This apps tells you the optimal hits for ceremonial sword smithing in the Artisan's Workshop in Falador.
Displays the last known full Nemi Forest map from /r/nemiforest subreddit
This app displays the locations of portable skilling locations according to Portables FC
This app solves Runedoku puzzle to get runes you can make about 1m/hr doing this.
This app is used to transcribe RuneScape lore from the game to other digital media.
Shows the minion order at Angel or Death
Tracks materials as they appear in the chat box.
FFXIV-inspired Job Gauge for Necromancy
